com.axibase.tsd.service.el.series.models

Class MultiCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.axibase.tsd.service.el.series.models.MultiCollection
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImmutableMultiCollection

    public abstract class MultiCollection
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulate groups of named series. Maintain sorted map of groups: series key -> series group. Each series group is an ordered Map: series name -> series. Series names are either explicitly generated in MVEL expression, or auto-generated in excel-like fashion: A, B, ..., Z, AA, AB, ...
